---
import "@fontsource/poppins"
import CTA from "../CTA.astro";
---

<section class="pd__inline">
    <div>
        <h1>Transformamos la realidad social de <span>escuelas rurales</span></h1>
        <p>Buscamos <span>acortar la desigualdad</span> de las infancias en las comunidades rurales en nuestro pa√≠s.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="center"><CTA /></div>
</section>
<style>
    section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        padding-block: 2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 5;
    }
    
	h1 {
		font-family: "Amatic SC", serif;
		font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    p {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1rem;
        width: 30ch;
    }

    span {
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .center,
        p {
            display: none;
        }
        
        div {
            display: grid;
            place-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 6rem;
        }
    }
</style>